headline: Maile Kaiser of CoreSite Honored as a CRN® Channel Chief
summary: DENVER, February 05, 2026--CoreSite, an American Tower company (NYSE: AMT) empowering critical business and AI workloads that impact everyday life through interconnected data center solutions, today announced that CRN®—a brand of The Channel Company—has selected Maile Kaiser, Chief Revenue Officer at CoreSite, for inclusion on the prestigious 2026 CRN® Channel Chiefs list.
